CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, August 2, 1938, pg. 18, reads: "Flash Cameraman Feted on Birthday - Surprise - Surprise, that was friends of Teeny [Teenie] Harris, News camera man had to say when they tossed a honey for him a Saturday ago. Wow, now whose party is this? One would think Harry Beale, who has merged himself with Helen Phillips (upper left), was the main man. (Photos by 'Teenie' Harris)."
TitMainTitle: Helen Phillips and Harry Beale embracing during birthday party for Charles "Teenie" Harris, in Loendi Club
